openssl (1.0.2-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release
    - Fixes CVE-2014-3571
    - Fixes CVE-2015-0206
    - Fixes CVE-2014-3569
    - Fixes CVE-2014-3572
    - Fixes CVE-2015-0204
